#Exception Handling : 
#Types of error are possible
#Syntax Errors
#Runtime Errors
#Exception handling is for runtime error only
#example of runtime error
#ZeroDivisionError
#Typeerror
#ValueError
#Filenotfounderror
#EOFError
#It is highly recommendation to use exception handling
#Graceful termination of program

#Example
try:
    read data from remote file locating at london
except FileNotFoundError:
    use local file and continue rest of the program normally

#Default exception handling :
#Terminating program abnormaly


